sequenceDiagram
  participant CLI as CLI
  participant Rewrite as story-localization.service
  participant Validate as generated-story-validator
  participant Analyze as story-production-analysis.service
  participant LLM as OpenAI
  participant Persist as workspace artifacts
  participant Episode as episode-commands
  participant TTS as speech provider
  participant Images as image-generation
  participant Render as renderer
  participant Meta as metadata service
  participant Publish as youtube-upload

  CLI->>Rewrite: stories rewrite-full --episode ...
  Rewrite->>Persist: materialize cleaned source
  Rewrite->>Persist: read/write facts cache
  Rewrite->>LLM: canonical full rewrite request
  alt cache hit
    Rewrite-->>CLI: reuse current artifact
  else cache miss
    LLM-->>Rewrite: structured rewrite response
    Rewrite->>Validate: validate narration package
    alt validation repair
      Validate-->>Rewrite: issues
      Rewrite->>LLM: repair or regenerate
      LLM-->>Rewrite: repaired response
    end
    Rewrite->>Persist: write canonical-full.json + script.md
  end

  CLI->>Analyze: stories analyze --episode ...
  Analyze->>Persist: resolve script + lineage
  Analyze->>LLM: structured production analysis
  LLM-->>Analyze: scores + findings
  Analyze->>Persist: write story-production-analysis.json
  alt BLOCKED
    Analyze-->>CLI: exit 1 with BLOCKED verdict
  else READY / READY_WITH_MINOR_EDITS
    Analyze-->>CLI: exit 0
  end

  CLI->>Episode: episode english|localized|short
  Episode->>Persist: parse source / write analysis artifacts
  Episode->>TTS: synthesize segment audio
  TTS-->>Episode: narration.wav
  Episode->>Persist: write narration-manifest + subtitles
  Episode->>Persist: write scenes.json
  Episode->>Images: generate/reuse scene images
  alt retryable provider failure
    Images->>LLM: image retry
    LLM-->>Images: image response
  end
  Images->>Persist: image manifests / checkpoints
  Episode->>Render: render clean video
  Render->>Persist: write render.json + mp4

  CLI->>Meta: metadata youtube
  Meta->>Persist: load scenes + narration dependency
  Meta->>LLM: metadata request
  LLM-->>Meta: metadata JSON
  Meta->>Persist: write youtube metadata outputs

  CLI->>Publish: youtube upload
  Publish->>Persist: resolve video + thumbnail + metadata
  Publish->>Publish: upload report idempotency check
  Publish->>LLM: optional metadata generation when --generate-metadata
  Publish->>Publish: call YouTube API
  Publish->>Persist: write youtube-upload.json
  Publish-->>CLI: uploaded / failed

